description:
◉◉ Submarine Arrow ◉◉

◉◉ Raise to the surface with your submarine escaping the sea dangers! ◉◉

Your submarine trip across the Pacific Ocean has been truncated!

You've gotten into trouble! You are in the most dangerous area of the sea!

Now you have to try to go up to the surface like an arrow with your submarine avoiding tricky trunks!

You can sky rocket as fast as an arrow or go slowly. Choose your strategy and keep your submarine rocket safe!

Collect the diamonds to unlock other submarines. They are amazing and surprising!

The longer you play the better you'll become at this escape game!

How long will you be able to survive in the sea?

Download this wonderful submarine rocket game and follow us on social networks!
